1.00	WSPG	WSPG	WSPG (1400AM/97.1 FM), known as "ESPN Spartanburg", is a sports radio station licensed to Spartanburg, South Carolina. It is owned by Jose Roberto and Aida Esperanza Ekonomo, though airtime is leased to Mark Hauser of Spartanburg Sports Media, LLC. The WSPG studios and transmitter are located at 340 Garner Road in Spartanburg.	
